column5: Hit some new product last night with the old lady and had a dream that I was fishing in Canada. Here is the prediction of the self proclaimed second smartest guy on Walleye Central Board. The border will open on July 2. I have run some statistical analysis and that is the date when the 75/25 vaccination dates will be met. Also, time for Americans to go spend some money. Also, lumber prices will drive the opening.
I will book a trip for July 3 and if it's not open I know who to blame
Who the heck is the smartest person on WC if you are the 2nd smartest... PjShorthorn
Obviously you, Pat! So, you got that going for you......
Big: If you are wrong - will you refund my deposit in Canadian or US funds ????????
Tip money for me, see previous post
On here, that distinguished honor would get ya a cup of coffee and a kick in the arse. PjShorthorn
